Really enjoy seeing shows here. The acoustics are great, the Phoenix Symphony is filled with such talent.  It is easy to get to by light rail, dropping you right on the corner with a very short walk to Symphony Hall.  There are lots of places to dine nearby before and after the show. Concessions at Symphony Hall are reasonable as well, you can bring your own water.

