Without a doubt the worst dining experience I have ever had. I ordered a wedge salad. The salad had all the makings of a wedge salad, but was not. With loads of dressing saturating the whole plate with lettuce in small pieces it was disguising.  The menu is so small you really did not have any healthy choices.  I asked if I could add a protein to the salad and was told they only have fried chicken, ok forget that.  We ended up just leaving and going to another restaurant nearby.

